Class CommonsLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.log.CommonsLog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InternalLogApi

    public class CommonsLog
extends Object
implements InternalLogApi
    Used to delegate internal logging of the signers and core classes to Jakarta Commons Logging.
